official_title: A bill to amend the Wild and Scenic Rivers Act of 1968 by designating a portion of the American River, Calif., for potential addition to the national wild and scenic rivers system.

summary.text: Designates a portion of the American River, California, for potential addition to the National Wild and Scenic Rivers System under the Wild and Scenic Rivers Act of 1968.
